Create topic:
--------------
kafka-topics --zookeeper 127.0.0.1:2181 --topic many-reps --create --partitions 6 --replication-factor 3

Describe topic:
---------------
kafka-topics --zookeeper 127.0.0.1:2181 --topic many-reps

Kafka console producer:
----------------------
kafka-console-producer --broker-list 127.0.0.1:9092,127.0.0.1:9093,127.0.0.1:9094 --topic many-reps

Kakfa console consumer:
-----------------------
kafka-console-consumer --bootstrap-server 127.0.0.1:9093 --topic many-reps --from-beginning

